Stay 
From Las Vegas to Lake Michigan and the Gulf Coast, Boyd Gaming offers the perfect place to stay, and so much more! We specialize in providing our guests with exceptional experiences. You can expect accommodations that are stylish, comfortable, relaxing and fun. Come stay with us, and experience Boyd Style for yourself. 	  
  Las Vegas
With more than 5,000 rooms situated across the Las Vegas Valley, Boyd Gaming’s seven hotels offer a variety of experiences to fit any desire and budget. 

 
  Illinois
Situated in central Illinois in East Peoria, the Par-A-Dice hotel features 202 rooms and suites and is the perfect place for a relaxing getaway or business retreat. 

 
  Indiana
The unparalleled Blue Chip Casino Hotel & Spa offers more than just a place to stay.  

 
  Louisiana
With more than 800 rooms, Boyd Gaming offers guests relaxing places to stay across the state of Louisiana. 

 
  Mississippi
Whether you’re visiting the Mid-South or the Gulf Coast, you’ll find an unforgettable experience awaiting you at our two Mississippi hotels. 

 








