B Connected 
 Earn Here • Redeem There • Enjoy Everywhere

It's Good To B Connected, and now you are at many of your favorite Boyd Gaming casinos throughout the U.S. B Connected is your bigger and better players club program. Bigger because now that you are connected to so many casino properties you can play at one and enjoy the use of your earned B Connected Points at another. Better because you now have many new ways to enjoy your B Connected Points from extra play on your favorite slots to extra values at your favorite restaurants to trips and much more.

There are three levels of B Connected to experience all with their own unique set of rewards and benefits. So whether you're just starting out as a Ruby Member, have progressed to being a Sapphire Member, or have made it all the way to becoming an Emerald Member you will find special ways to be treated and ways to earn special treats.

Now over a dozen of your favorite Boyd Gaming casinos - from Las Vegas to Louisiana to Illinois and Indiana to Mississippi - are all connected. Earn at one . . . enjoy at another . . . all with one great card. It's that easy - and rewarding!

So make sure you always play with your B Connected card and you'll be well on your way to enjoying the special B Connected privileges and benefits at so many terrific Boyd Gaming casinos throughout the country. And remember, It's Good To B Connected!

View our Privacy Policy.  








