Boyd e-Sourcing Tools (BeST)




 Welcome to the Boyd Gaming's e-Sourcing Tool or BeST System.  
			       By utilizing the power of the  Internet, we now provide additional 
			       avenues to connect and transact commerce with both  current and potential 
			       suppliers.  The goal of the BeST system is to provide more efficient 
			       ways for both the Company and  its suppliers to communicate and conduct 
			       business.  As we  move forward, please take note of our continued 
			       enhancements to the BeST System.




Through the website you can:

Complete an electronic application to do Business with Boyd Gaming 
				    Corporation properties
You will be able to manage and update your account information as needed
Review our purchasing policies and business requirements
Review information regarding our economic development initiatives for 
                    women and minority owned businesses





For BeST results the acceptable browsers are as follows:
          Internet Explorer 8
		                     Internet Explorer 9
		                     Firefox
		                     Chrome






