Sam's Town Las VegasIf you're ready for fun, then you're ready for Sam's Town Hotel & Gambling Hall in Las Vegas! Choose a hotel room overlooking Mystic Falls Indoor Park or opt for a view of the glittering city lights and majestic mountains surrounding the Las Vegas Valley. Spread across three levels, Sam's Town has all your favorite games and offers terrific odds on our single-deck blackjack tables and 20x odds on craps. Once you check into Sam's town, you will find all the comforts you need to make it the perfect getaway!


Courtesy shuttle to The Strip and Downtown
645 elegantly appointed rooms and suites
56-lane bowling center featuring BES-X Entertainment System
Multiple restaurants & food outlets
600-seat Bingo Parlor
Poker Room
State-of-the-art Race & Sports Book
Roxy's live entertainment nightly
30,000 square feet of tastefully appointed banquet & meeting space
18-screen movie theater complex with THX Sound and stadium seating
Mystic Falls Indoor Park featuring Sunset Stampede Laser Light Show
Free parking in three covered parking structures plus valet service
Fitness center for hotel guests
Tropical Pool area open year round

Take A Tour






























































 




 
 





