Eastside Cannery Casino & HotelConveniently located just off Boulder Highway and only 7 miles from McCarran International Airport, Eastside Cannery Casino & Hotel has become the favorite of area residents for gaming fun, dining value, and star-studded entertainment. With 65,000-square-feet of gaming space, restaurants, and amenities, Eastside Cannery is a world of thrills, delights, and comfort.
