Boyd Gaming Corp.


            
            Boyd Gaming Corp. engages in the management and operation of gaming and entertainment properties. It operates through the following business segments: Las Vegas Locals, Downtown Las Vegas, Midwest and South, Peninsula, and Borgata. Its portfolio includes hotels, casino, breweries, resorts, and spa. The company was founded by William Samuel Boyd and Sam Boyd on January 1, 1975 and is headquartered in Las Vegas, NV.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  




